Complete PHP migration script for JailTrak v2.0 that creates database backup, applies schema_v2.sql, prompts for admin account creation with username/email/password, creates default user preferences, generates 3 default invite codes (ADMIN-2025-MASTER unlimited, BETA-USER-2025 50 uses, TEAM-ACCESS-01 20 uses), displays migration statistics showing counts of users/inmates/charges/invites/logs, shows next steps including login URL, and handles rollback on errors.